---
import astroLogo from '../assets/astro.svg';
---

<div class="container">
  <div class="gradient-background">
    <div class="apple-gradient">
      <div class="blob blob1"></div>
      <div class="blob blob2"></div>
      <div class="blob blob3"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <main>
    <p class="korean-copy">
      이곳은 개인의 상상력이 모여 훌륭한 작업을 이끄는 가치에 헌신하는 곳입니다. 여기서는 단순히 합류하는 것이 아니라, <span class="highlight">당신만의 색깔로 세상을 바꿔나갈 것입니다.</span>
    </p>
  </main>
</div>

<style>
  @import url(//spoqa.github.io/spoqa-han-sans/css/SpoqaHanSansNeo.css);

  /* Reset and base styles */
  * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  :root {
    --primary: #4d21fc;
    --secondary: #7828c8;
    --accent: #f41cf4;
    --background: #F8FAFC;
    --text: #000000;
    --text-light: #ffffff;
    --text-muted: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
    --radius: 12px;
    --shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    --gradient-scale-mid: 0.6;
    --gradient-scale-final: 1.1;
  }

  /* Container layout with responsive height */
  .container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 650px; /* Fixed height instead of vh for better control */
    padding: 16px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Updated gradient background */
  .gradient-background {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    z-index: -1;
    background-color: #F8FAFC;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .apple-gradient {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: -1;
    filter: saturate(1.05);
    will-change: transform, opacity;
  }

  .blob {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: scale(0.2);
    filter: blur(100px);
    animation: blob-expand 4s ease-out forwards, blob-drift 14s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }

  .blob1 {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 25% 30%, #A6D5FF 0%, transparent 75%);
    animation-delay: 0s;
  }

  .blob2 {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 70% 65%, #FFD1A6 0%, transparent 70%);
    animation-delay: 0.5s;
  }

  .blob3 {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, #A7F3D0 0%, transparent 75%);
    animation-delay: 0.3s;
  }

  @keyframes blob-expand {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: scale(0.2);
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 0.6;
      transform: scale(0.9);
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: scale(1.4);
    }
  }

  @keyframes blob-drift {
    from {
      transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0) scale(1.4);
    }
    to {
      transform: translate3d(10px, -10px, 0) scale(1.5);
    }
  }

  /* Add soft noise texture */
  .apple-gradient::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 200 200' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.75' numOctaves='2' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.03'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .korean-copy {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 5.5vw, 42px);
    line-height: 1.5;
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 600;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-family: 'Spoqa Han Sans Neo', system-ui, sans-serif;
    word-break: keep-all;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    text-shadow: 0 1px 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  .highlight {
    color: #000;
    position: relative;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* Position the text */
  main {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 3;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  /* Responsive adjustments for devices */
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    /* Tablet */
    .container {
      min-height: 500px;
    }
    
    .korean-copy {
      font-size: clamp(32px, 6vw, 48px);
      max-width: 900px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    /* Desktop */
    .container {
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    
    .korean-copy {
      font-size: clamp(38px, 7vw, 58px);
      max-width: 1100px;
      line-height: 1.35;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    /* Small mobile */
    .container {
      min-height: 450px;
    }
    
    .korean-copy {
      font-size: clamp(24px, 5vw, 32px);
      line-height: 1.6;
      padding: 0 15px;
    }
  }
</style>
